docs.lead_paragraph: Two hundred and seventy-two Harlem landlords have been directed to appear in court next week to answer charges that they failed to rid their buildings of rats or conditions causing rats.

headline.main: 272 Slum Owners Given Summonses On Rat Infestation

docs.abstract: 272 Harlem landlords summoned for failure to end rat-breeding conditions; Ct fines 612 W 137th St owner and lessee $850 for 97 violations
